# CODEOWNERS — kagent-workshop
#
# Enforces the per-UC ownership boundary required by NFR-008 of
# kagent-workshop-scenarios (and the team's "1 UC par dev" policy from the
# product brief). Last-match-wins: the per-UC rules below override the
# default-fallback `*` rule for files inside `scenarios/uc<N>/`.
#
# ⚠ Verify the GitHub handles before the first PR opens. CODEOWNERS silently
#   does nothing for unrecognised handles — the worst failure mode for an
#   anti-collision policy. The handles below are the architecture-doc
#   placeholders and may need updating to match the team's real GitHub usernames.

# Default fallback — both authors review anything not matched below.
